Class ComposedImagingMeasurementConfigurationDTO

java.lang.Object
  ch.ethz.csb.youscope.shared.configuration.MeasurementConfigurationDTO
      ch.ethz.csb.youscope.shared.configuration.composedimaging.ComposedImagingMeasurementConfigurationDTO
All Implemented Interfaces:
Configuration, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
public class ComposedImagingMeasurementConfigurationDTO
extends MeasurementConfigurationDTO

This class represents a measurement which takes images in a two dimensional spatial array, such that the single pictures can be afterwards composed to a single big one.

Author:
Moritz Lang
